Alibaba-NTU Singapore Joint Research Institute invites applications for the position of Research Fellow.
Key Responsibilities:

  Carry out research in the field of online recommendation system, bandit learning, and multi-objective optimization
  Help to prepare and submit project proposals related to personalized recommendation systems
  Write papers and reports based on the requirements of the projects
  Present research outputs at academic conferences, seminars, and workshops

Job Requirements:

  PhD degree in Computer Science or Computational Mathematics
  Strong background in numerical computation methods, multi-objective optimization algorithms, matrix computation, and bandit learning for developing online recommendation systems for E-commerce platforms
  Strong publication record in reputable conferences and journals
  Familiar with Python and PyTorch

We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.